166","parent":"160","text":"6. RS3PE (sinovitis simétrica seronegativa con edema)","guid":"7vv4N38Jtbu52_giIpE81w","children":[]}]},{"id":"167","parent":"156","text":"- Diagnóstico diferencial:","guid":"x08vUsiFOvNQrVP9Ir90og","children":[{"id":"168","parent":"167","text":"→ Descartar síndromes paraneoplásicos y metástasis óseas","guid":"w18NXYG6l8uGGpe1HEQLVQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"169","parent":"156","text":"- Serologías:","guid":"l1Z_mRs-9EzzOjYJYnsbpw","children":[{"id":"170","parent":"169","text":"→ Factor reumatoide y anticuerpos antipéptidos citrulinados negativos","guid":"FFeVgUQ5awMxbbONwP2RiA","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"169","text":"→ Posibilidad de ANA positivo","guid":"8jWs-k_rQrC16ZyK0b8_Wg","children":[]}]},{"id":"172","parent":"156","text":"- Duración:","guid":"Nayp4Nurm82fYMQidX_LJw","children":[{"id":"173","parent":"172","text":"→ Puede persistir >2 años post-terapia","guid":"jSyzUFvc-irHb970v4nF_A","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"172","text":"→ Requiere tratamiento inmunosupresor continuo","guid":"_A4Qo7iRqPcgwYbcXoHtyQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"175","parent":"156","text":"Manejo de artritis\\Ninflamatoria por irAE:","guid":"bMZjdnmogls78DG9eTzhAA","children":[{"id":"176","parent":"175","text":"- Corticosteroides en dosis altas","guid":"bYWVfSD3Af8siDQZqjPo9g","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"175","text":"- Inicio temprano\\Nde DMARDs o\\Nbiológicos si\\Nprednisona >10\\Nmg/día no se\\Nreduce","guid":"mXyoF-aNza5UHVnsTnv8zA","children":[{"id":"178","parent":"177","text":"Hidroxicloroquina, sulfasalazina,\\Nmetotrexato, leflunomida, tofacitinib","guid":"2byrlJ0UADquvw5FOm1nrg","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"177","text":"- Biológicos","guid":"zfyoOthztENTCwpAVCQjRg","children":[{"id":"180","parent":"179","text":"inhibidores de TNF-alfa, tocilizumab","guid":"UYsMWQ0xFj_Ouvyn6pyjuA","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"179","text":"Aprimilast y secukinumab\\Npara artritis psoriásica","guid":"Wvry1gZBQi4m9UwV0R43LA","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"182","parent":"156","text":"Notas","guid":"clIGGsVw7AFulDovLJhCxA","children":[{"id":"183","parent":"182","text":"- Tratamiento con DMARDs y biológicos no asociado a progresión tumoral","guid":"BV2RH1M4btXheWn4xb6b7Q","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"182","text":"- EULAR recomienda inhibidores de TNF-alfa o tocilizumab\\Nsobre otros biológicos para artritis inflamatoria asociada a ICI","guid":"5eWgnWvJzw8i_nRZmL6n0Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"185","parent":"0","text":"Título: Polimialgia Reumática\\N(PMR) inducida por ICIs","guid":"b7lD22DLoPoJb1diVqCSEw","children":[{"id":"186","parent":"185","text":"- Características","guid":"MZTW0N6K_w13Kt0aQT0NrQ","children":[{"id":"187","parent":"186","text":"→ Común como irAE musculoesquelético","guid":"3iBboYJPICuEFntCDrtPSg","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"186","text":"→ Inicio súbito de rigidez y dolor muscular proximal","guid":"QI-kTobQWedysnXQSG_Cmw","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"186","text":"→ No siempre cumple criterios ACR/EULAR","guid":"cZ5QmVPXiktlmsm3b_28Rw","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"186","text":"→ Marcadores inflamatorios pueden estar normales","guid":"lpsQyZxuWBCzUlZLVGbnuQ","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"186","text":"→ Características atípicas: FR y CCP positivos, sinovitis en articulaciones periféricas","guid":"D4OR_crutmg3tLN0R0gjxw","children":[]}]},{"id":"192","parent":"185","text":"- Manejo:","guid":"4aDb2Oog0e2J3g0CTQYbHg","children":[{"id":"193","parent":"192","text":"→ Casos reportados:","guid":"rMSd1tS5BeRQRJk4yQCGOw","children":[{"id":"194","parent":"193","text":"- Más de un tercio requiere >20 mg de prednisona/día","guid":"R0zykduk0hVxdhEvTn9phQ","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"193","text":"- Otros con 5–7.5 mg/día controlan síntomas","guid":"b3GXbXHu0-PHOlWBz-em1g","children":[]}]},{"id":"196","parent":"192","text":"→ Algunos responden solo a AINEs","guid":"XHnMLaGcQ4AAYx71BU3Okw","children":[]}]},{"id":"197","parent":"185","text":"- Recomendaciones\\Nde tratamiento:","guid":"GTKvPmC_06jgUtNLFVndWw","children":[{"id":"198","parent":"197","text":"→ 10–20 mg de prednisona/día para toxicidad grado 2","guid":"ZRz7D1FnOghdBM5lCVo3GQ","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"197","text":"→ 40 mg de prednisona/día y considerar DMARDs para grado 3–4","guid":"L8w4socB9xkV3DyqnzsJoA","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"197","text":"→ Usar agentes ahorradores de esteroides si no se reduce a <10 mg de prednisona/día","guid":"fGnVmyOY14GN38mMd6W97g","children":[]}]},{"id":"201","parent":"185","text":"- Terapias específicas:","guid":"QC_5-VcwrHBrfAyW3eX17A","children":[{"id":"202","parent":"201","text":"→ Tocilizumab efectivo en casos de PMR inducida por ICIs","guid":"wChIdT9DM3AKp91Jz5XmBA","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"201","text":"→ Otros DMARDs como hidroxicloroquina y metotrexato también han sido exitosos","guid":"f2p2Y2SfF8I5Z7UgMYAwFQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"204","parent":"0","text":"Título: Síndrome Sicca\\Ninducido por ICIs","guid":"P3qQDLSQTAjXA_Xya5uI6Q","children":[{"id":"205","parent":"204","text":"- Incidencia","guid":"scLLfmh7XWtpskmPfanD_g","children":[{"id":"206","parent":"205","text":"→ Ojos secos y boca seca: 3-24%","guid":"xK321tI0GtGZRiEtP_UwhA","children":[]}]},{"id":"207","parent":"204","text":"Síndrome Sicca por ICIs:","guid":"T6s-FAteNVxvN2v8KClSzA","children":[{"id":"208","parent":"207","text":"→ Inicio abrupto, usualmente <3 meses después de iniciar ICIs","guid":"HDE7WIm8OF52X0VwZQrs4g","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"207","text":"→ Predominio en hombres y mayor edad de inicio","guid":"MDJo-IAXjidzCZeOxpcRcg","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"207","text":"→ Bajas tasas de anticuerpos asociados (SSA, SSB, factor reumatoide, ANA)","guid":"VOvxds5oBMllDKTYeaOXQw","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"207","text":"→ Mejoría con corticosteroides","guid":"eSvcohATwLAej1kOTDxFFw","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"207","text":"→ Biopsia de glándula salival muestra infiltrado linfocítico T","guid":"CGUwi9KcBQAhoBJJqztBKw","children":[]}]},{"id":"213","parent":"204","text":"- Sintomatología\\Ny manejo:","guid":"K7bqV5zxvDg5EevA_fr__A","children":[{"id":"214","parent":"213","text":"→ Síntomas leves: cuidado oral básico, sustitutos de saliva tópicos, lágrimas\\Nartificiales, caramelos sin azúcar, secretagogos (cevimelina o pilocarpina)","guid":"CIzQFEOo9J0d7o1kKM2DNA","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"213","text":"→ Síntomas severos o intolerables: inicio de terapia con prednisona","guid":"tpE3gtRHe4G--Zr9jy22ZA","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"213","text":"→ Déficit prolongado de flujo salival en muchos casos","guid":"RsHJnZDYAweFRL52wTMLEA","children":[]}]},{"id":"217","parent":"204","text":"- Decisión sobre\\Ncontinuación de ICIs:","guid":"noJhfb9J7Afh6oFbzLx4WQ","children":[{"id":"218","parent":"217","text":"→ Varía según el caso","guid":"ZdmP1ObsUcaaRE4KPrA8Bg","children":[]},{"id":"219","parent":"217","text":"→ Mejoría con corticosteroides en la mayoría","guid":"AwspiNi33yLPnhN7T31N3w","children":[]}]},{"id":"220","parent":"204","text":"- Comparación con\\NSíndrome de Sjogren:","guid":"P8UUM9XMSbXyTqJIacswjg","children":[{"id":"221","parent":"220","text":"→ DMARDs no son eficaces para sicca-irAE","guid":"_DPqIDnBHlZnnaIzuwbBUQ","children":[]},{"id":"222","parent":"220","text":"→ No se recomiendan DMARDs","guid":"QAC1Z0MDnwZPp7p9N44cSw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"223","parent":"0","text":"Título: Esclerodermia\\NInducida por ICIs","guid":"svDMn0RQNE_5lXlRrEoy4g","children":[{"id":"224","parent":"223","text":"- Presentación:","guid":"5O3vCwLS4LFxx0Aikk3DyQ","children":[{"id":"225","parent":"224","text":"→ Casos de esclerosis sistémica difusa sin afectación de órganos internos","guid":"cBuKwm3cEHnNNdTzanaxQA","children":[]},{"id":"226","parent":"224","text":"→ Esclerosis sistémica limitada con fenómeno de Raynaud","guid":"VBmls4RT2lNeMPoFeYTO0A","children":[]}]},{"id":"227","parent":"223","text":"- Serologías y marcadores:","guid":"kpvxXgbpyT5lIEpkOB00yw","children":[{"id":"228","parent":"227","text":"→ ANA, anticentromero, antitopoisomerasa (Scl-70) negativos","guid":"WPV6tiPFt1rBRdW9rkiGHQ","children":[]},{"id":"229","parent":"227","text":"→ Marcadores inflamatorios variables","guid":"EWTRrSwm-zmqEhUv92M-Mw","children":[]}]},{"id":"230","parent":"223","text":"- Cronología:","guid":"lR9n4pe_gDoOOBAuVu8e0g","children":[{"id":"231","parent":"230","text":"→ Inicio mediano de síntomas: 395 días post-administración del ICI","guid":"7k4hBifzackakUNfyD8LEA","children":[]}]},{"id":"232","parent":"223","text":"- Tratamiento:","guid":"w3Rng1WfxtFaEduqcjU6xA","children":[{"id":"233","parent":"232","text":"→ Cese de ICIs","guid":"btICIm4chU0fghSos_iUBA","children":[]},{"id":"234","parent":"232","text":"→ Prednisona alta dosis: 1 mg/kg/día","guid":"hqXEbBa3833qUyJWI4s7Bg","children":[]},{"id":"235","parent":"232","text":"→ Inmunosupresión variable: IVIG, hidroxicloroquina, micofenolato mofetil","guid":"gx_Yl67MK9U3mbVm7Sy6tg","children":[]}]},{"id":"236","parent":"223","text":"- Resultados:","guid":"p4g50W9Us4tWUhH3W9Ne5w","children":[{"id":"237","parent":"236","text":"→ Mejora en engrosamiento y tensión de la piel","guid":"sZT8omM5gjvIk6vZ5lpgcw","children":[]},{"id":"238","parent":"236","text":"→ Un paciente falleció por causas no cancerosas desconocidas meses después","guid":"efrZSmx40pOHu4tIamJ7Zw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"239","parent":"0","text":"Título: Miositis y\\NMiocarditis Inducidas por\\NICIs","guid":"xT06y8OdhJm0Cmq2JtTEUg","children":[{"id":"240","parent":"239","text":"- Miositis","guid":"nkM60tvKFXpfvWsKRfxbGg","children":[{"id":"241","parent":"240","text":"→ Incidencia: 0.15-0.24%","guid":"uUy5LL5BDDxOY211Hlo0Pg","children":[]},{"id":"242","parent":"240","text":"→ Inicio temprano: 25-31 días post-ICI","guid":"X-SkyJkVZYFlst0fX19oQQ","children":[]},{"id":"243","parent":"240","text":"→ Predominio masculino","guid":"LyTWCIsfp3Z5lNnNJj7ElA","children":[]},{"id":"244","parent":"240","text":"→ Síntomas: dolor muscular, debilidad proximal\\Nsimétrica, disfagia, disfonía, debilidad respiratoria","guid":"pqEq8pLVmSOTFj2xE5Bfgg","children":[]},{"id":"245","parent":"240","text":"→ Sin cambios cutáneos típicos, posible dermatomiositis","guid":"gQ7Abe6yg7Gx-hb90jxRcQ","children":[]},{"id":"246","parent":"240","text":"→ Evaluar miastenia gravis si hay ptosis o debilidad ocular","guid":"iFfMT-PYq1YSzXXXsr_kxw","children":[]},{"id":"247","parent":"240","text":"→ Laboratorio: aumento CK, aldolasa, transaminasas, LDH","guid":"hYbtxXTmBXZNQ_jjHQU3WQ","children":[]},{"id":"248","parent":"240","text":"→ Biopsia muscular: cambios miopáticos necrotizantes","guid":"YKgPis611rztJTGWJ5yaDQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"249","parent":"239","text":"- Manejo","guid":"YIprBWlCgG6eUbVbSmKpIQ","children":[{"id":"250","parent":"249","text":"→ Interrumpir ICIs","guid":"F1zAfm28c4SCcL9CZlRSgA","children":[]},{"id":"251","parent":"249","text":"→ Corticosteroides altas dosis: 1 mg/kg/día prednisona\\No metilprednisolona 1 g/3-5 días","guid":"5JVegEefzMlLDthXvJTRRQ","children":[]},{"id":"252","parent":"249","text":"→ IVIG y plasmaféresis en enfermedad severa","guid":"UCUYPUhosuMED5aEeiCKmw","children":[]},{"id":"253","parent":"249","text":"→ DMARDs: metotrexato, micofenolato mofetilo, azatioprina","guid":"TaoziJTvI5Xkpn8ECclsyA","children":[]},{"id":"254","parent":"249","text":"→ Biológicos: infliximab (baja tasa de éxito), tocilizumab","guid":"C36E9HoTHuKiBwA3GAPPYA","children":[]}]},{"id":"255","parent":"239","text":"- Miocarditis","guid":"BiCp2DyEPX_a8noYbCmiJA","children":[{"id":"256","parent":"255","text":"→ Complicación grave con alta morbilidad","guid":"TOzQBN1O_KLyghL0qIo4cg","children":[]},{"id":"257","parent":"255","text":"→ Mortalidad: 24% en miositis, 56.7% con miocarditis concurrente","guid":"IuNDM4rlpQm1q1Krumkmrw","children":[]},{"id":"258","parent":"255","text":"→ Diagnóstico: síntomas de falla cardiaca, troponinas, ECG, ecocardiograma, RM cardiaca","guid":"fckZCAxr4TQwAuiXHFWTRg","children":[]}]},{"id":"259","parent":"239","text":"- Manejo de\\Nmiocarditis:","guid":"nN-qhhbJbeF5hysnzJsplg","children":[{"id":"260","parent":"259","text":"→ Enfoque agresivo con DMARDs o biológicos temprano","guid":"fzeGVYjB7o-iIw8M07KHfA","children":[]},{"id":"261","parent":"259","text":"→ Abatacept en casos refractarios, pero puede afectar respuesta tumoral","guid":"NAw2-KapT9zm-k7O7zJdzg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"262","parent":"0","text":"Título: Vasculitis\\NInducida por ICIs","guid":"ssjCKb_gbq5a5QhGmeAaog","children":[{"id":"263","parent":"262","text":"- Incidencia y presentación:","guid":"CVP7XrxM3JHH2nPqVkV84A","children":[{"id":"264","parent":"263","text":"→ Rara: 0.26% en estudios de farmacovigilancia","guid":"ZyyxSPl-Q8gzBA3C1q7Lug","children":[]},{"id":"265","parent":"263","text":"→ Tipos: pequeños, medianos y grandes vasos","guid":"7ZsJqzEEEOTbKjb43_LlQg","children":[]},{"id":"266","parent":"263","text":"→ Específicos: arteritis de células gigantes (GCA), peri-aortitis, vasculitis de\\Nórgano único (testicular, renal), cutánea leucocitoclástica, vasculitis del SNC","guid":"fIqbXtwlo7erIXX_DF17dQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"267","parent":"262","text":"- Mortalidad y\\Ncomplicaciones:","guid":"TxggQ82lTi1d4R7Ci2p_lg","children":[{"id":"268","parent":"267","text":"→ Mortalidad asociada: 6%","guid":"MxiFW_CQNzKE5yxUdsTLYA","children":[]},{"id":"269","parent":"267","text":"→ En GCA, cerca del 30% desarrolló ceguera","guid":"XGI-axccxGflPdqDnNugRA","children":[]}]},{"id":"270","parent":"262","text":"- Serologías:","guid":"NGgwUizyHOKgsVn503uxAg","children":[{"id":"271","parent":"270","text":"→ ANCA, frecuentemente negativos","guid":"A3glrQH_sgjtjU0HjTNm7w","children":[]},{"id":"272","parent":"270","text":"→ ANCA positivo no implica peor pronóstico en vasculitis de pequeños vasos","guid":"JcmFcVnQpO-hGzJSfLvAMw","children":[]}]},{"id":"273","parent":"262","text":"- Tratamiento:","guid":"DnhUsQR3mwD-mrvcDREVtQ","children":[{"id":"274","parent":"273","text":"→ Retirada de ICI","guid":"gXI7X7Rpw-CqLumqMrtTYg","children":[]},{"id":"275","parent":"273","text":"→ Corticosteroides en dosis altas","guid":"Td6d6i5ajRf8kmwILfXw6A","children":[]},{"id":"276","parent":"273","text":"→ Ciclofosfamida oral y rituximab en vasculitis ANCA-asociada (AAV)","guid":"6kmycHZU4cvtu57Y22SOlA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"277","parent":"0","text":"Enfermedad Autoinmune\\NPreexistente e irAEs","guid":"7UkfrHnY7rxgjwGh_vUFPA","children":[{"id":"278","parent":"277","text":"- Contexto:","guid":"EzoV0PuRxMEKvSYgvApviQ","children":[{"id":"279","parent":"278","text":"→ Datos limitados: pacientes con enfermedad autoinmune excluidos de ensayos","guid":"-uoeM0vijgA1-RbIw2mBUw","children":[]},{"id":"280","parent":"278","text":"→ Revisión sistemática de\\N123 pacientes mostró:","guid":"XfL6cutLal_HOpYO8vJrWA","children":[{"id":"281","parent":"280","text":"- irAEs 75% con enfermedad autoinmune previa","guid":"-CVnVXZjsO3zkUixQcMykA","children":[]},{"id":"282","parent":"280","text":"- Empeoramiento de enfermedad autoinmune en 50%","guid":"FyhkdwRapU1Zhn9yyt6lmw","children":[]},{"id":"283","parent":"280","text":"- irAEs de novo en 34%","guid":"VS7ac7femi7-Zf8__EDpxw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"284","parent":"277","text":"- Relación con\\Ntipos de ICIs:","guid":"QpSG3gYxiO-VFqgeEw_EWQ","children":[{"id":"285","parent":"284","text":"→ Inhibidores PD-1 y PD-L1: más recaídas de enfermedad subyacente","guid":"gchdRh34YpaHPC8-p1sC8A","children":[]},{"id":"286","parent":"284","text":"→ Ipilimumab (inhibidor CTLA-4): más irAEs de novo","guid":"nZLIRgCXdZLOAJZ1vb3NSA","children":[]}]},{"id":"287","parent":"277","text":"- Enfermedad\\Nreumática preexistente:","guid":"VvksLBA3wNQnlbTmeqYj-g","children":[{"id":"288","parent":"287","text":"→ Artritis reumatoide: 35% tuvo recaída de artritis,\\N25% desarrolló irAEs de novo, 15% ambos","guid":"sN1U4cmgLDrY8h4iEMLCEg","children":[]}]},{"id":"289","parent":"277","text":"- Respuesta antitumoral:","guid":"V0uTTChaiOCQzIVXcdhl6g","ch